badges.name: VSRE I
badges.description: Salesforce Verified Security Risk Expert Level I
badges.criteria: 1. Recipient must have a security role/responsibility and demonstrate exceptional security knowledge and skill. 2. A valid FIRST CVSS 4.0 certification is required. The next step in this path is VSRE II. * The next step in this path is VSRE III.

badges.name: VSRE II
badges.description: Salesforce Verified Security Risk Expert Level II
badges.criteria: 1. SFDC Security/Risk/Compliance/Audit role of: Senior (SMTS) / Lead (LMTS)  / Principal (PMTS) / Director (and above) / BISO. 2. Valid ISC2 CISSP certification. 3. Valid FIRST CVSS 4.0 certification. 4. Other certifications for considerations. * The next step in this path is VSRE III.

badges.name: VSRE III
badges.description: Salesforce Verified Security Risk Expert Level III
badges.criteria: 1. SFDC Security/Risk/Compliance/Audit role of: Senior (SMTS) / Lead (LMTS)  / Principal (PMTS) / Director (and above) / BISO. 2. Valid ISC2 CISSP certification. 3. Valid ISC2 ISSAP certification. 4. Valid ISACA CISA certification. 5. Valid FIRST CVSS 4.0 certification.
